      • rewind

        public Parcel rewind()
        Rewinds this parcel and sets the position to 0. Invoke this method before a sequence of channel-write or get operations, assuming that the limit has already been set appropriately. For example: 
           int i = 0;
   parcel.add(i);     // Add data.
   buf.rewind();      // Rewind the parcel.
   buf.getInt();      // Read the added data.
        Returns:
        Return the current parcel for chained invocation.
